# EduCore — Implementation Plan
### Web-Based Tuition Institution Management System

---

## Overview

Build a full-stack, web-based management system for tuition institutions. Institution owners install it on their PC (runs locally via `npm start`) or self-host it. The app supports 5 roles with strict RBAC.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a **locally-run web app** — the institution owner runs `npm run start` to launch it in a browser on `localhost:3000`. No internet hosting required. Data stays on their machine (SQLite file). If you want cloud hosting instead, we can switch the DB to PostgreSQL later.

> [!NOTE]
> For Phase 1 we'll build the **complete core system** (all 5 dashboards functional). Advanced features like PDF export, SMS alerts, and AI insights come after the core is validated.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| **Framework** | Next.js 15 (App Router) | Full-stack, routing, SSR, API routes |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui | Rapid beautiful UI |
| **Database** | SQLite via Prisma ORM | Zero-config local DB, single file |
| **Auth** | NextAuth.js v5 (credentials) | Role-based sessions |
| **Charts** | Recharts | Student/class analytics |
| **Forms** | React Hook Form + Zod | Validation |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | Consistent icons |
| **Notifications** | In-app (DB-driven) | No external service needed |
| **PDF** | React-PDF / jsPDF | Report cards |

---

