### Auth & Registration

#### [NEW] `src/app/(auth)/register/page.tsx`
Multi-step institution registration wizard:
1. Institution info (name, address, logo)
2. Owner personal info (name, email, phone)
3. Set owner password
4. Confirmation → creates Institution + Owner account in DB

#### [NEW] `src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx`
- Single login page for ALL roles
- After login → middleware redirects to role-specific dashboard
- Shows institution name in header

#### [NEW] `src/middleware.ts`
- Protect all dashboard routes
- Role-based redirect (owner → /owner, worker → /worker, etc.)

---

